headline: FedEx Struggles, Micron Stock Rips Up Ahead Of Earnings; Highflying Drone Maker Set For Turnaround
summary: Micron stock has doubled since hitting a low of 61.54 in early April. Earnings expectations are high as the company stays in growth mode.

headline: 1 Large-Cap Stock to Research Further and 2 to Turn Down
summary: Large-cap stocks are known for their staying power and ability to weather market storms better than smaller competitors. However, their sheer size makes it more challenging to maintain high growth rates as they’ve already captured significant portions of their markets.
